st scan (PDF, XML, JSON etc).</span>[/ultimate_icon_list_item][ultimate_icon_list_item icon_type=\"custom\" icon_img=\"id^191|url^http://scopun.co.uk/projects/catering1/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Screen-Shot-2017-09-25-at-2.40.34-PM.png|caption^null|alt^null|title^Screen-Shot-2017-09-25-at-2.40.34-PM|description^null\" el_class=\"iconstyle\"]<strong> 2FA </strong>\r\n<span style=\"color: #8d9395;\">Two-factor authentication for all users in the team.</span>[/ultimate_icon_list_item][/ultimate_icon_list][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1537260966092{border-top-width: 1px !important;border-right-width: 1px !important;border-bottom-width: 1px !important;border-left-width: 1px !important;border-left-color: #f36c21 !important;border-left-style: solid !important;border-right-color: #f36c21 !important;border-right-style: solid !important;border-top-color: #f36c21 !important;border-top-style: solid !important;border-bottom-color: #f36c21 !important;border-bottom-style: solid !important;}\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"Standard\" font_container=\"tag:h1|text_align:center\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">No of menus: UNLIMITED</span></em></strong></p>\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2 class=\"mainpricenumber\">£100<span class=\"permonths\">/Per month</span></h2>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Reporting, automation &amp; integrations for support teams</p>\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][us_btn text=\"CONTINUE\" link=\"url:http%3A%2F%2Fscopun.co.uk%2Fprojects%2Fcatering1%2Fthank-you%2F|||\" style=\"outlined\" align=\"center\"][vc_empty_space][vc_row_inner css=\".vc_custom_1506332168908{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;background-color: #eeeeee !important;}\"][vc_column_inner][vc_column_text el_class=\"headel\"]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Everything in standard</strong> plus:</p>\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_empty_space height=\"20px\"][ultimate_icon_list el_class=\"padprice\"][ultimate_icon_list_item icon_type=\"custom\" icon_img=\"id^191|url^http://scopun.co.uk/projects/catering1/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Screen-Shot-2017-09-25-at-2.40.34-PM.png|caption^null|alt^null|title^Screen-Shot-2017-09-25-at-2.40.34-PM|description^null\" el_class=\"iconstyle\"]<strong>Professional team functionality</strong>\r\n<span style=\"color: #8d9395;\">Invite up to 10 team members with up to 10 scan profiles.</span>[/ultimate_icon_list_item][ultimate_icon_list_item icon_type=\"custom\" icon_img=\"id^191|url^http://scopun.co.uk/projects/catering1/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Screen-Shot-2017-09-25-at-2.40.34-PM.png|caption^null|alt^null|title^Screen-Shot-2017-09-25-at-2.40.34-PM|description^null\" el_class=\"iconstyle\"]<strong>Scan as logged in</strong>\r\n<span style=\"color: #8d9395;\">Support for setup of scanning behind logins and more complex authentication.</span>[/ultimate_icon_list_item][ultimate_icon_list_item icon_type=\"custom\" icon_img=\"id^191|url^http://scopun.co.uk/projects/catering1/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Screen-Shot-2017-09-25-at-2.40.34-PM.png|caption^null|alt^null|title^Screen-Shot-2017-09-25-at-2.40.34-PM|description^null\" el_class=\"iconstyle\"]<strong>API integration</strong>\r\n<span style=\"color: #8d9395;\">Start, stop and check status of scans.</span>[/ultimate_icon_list_item][ultimate_icon_list_item icon_type=\"custom\" icon_img=\"id^191|url^http://scopun.co.uk/projects/catering1/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Screen-Shot-2017-09-25-at-2.40.34-PM.png|caption^null|alt^null|title^Screen-Shot-2017-09-25-at-2.40.34-PM|description^null\" el_class=\"iconstyle\"]<strong>Premium support </strong>\r\n<span style=\"color: #8d9395;\">Answer within 48 hours.</span>[/ultimate_icon_list_item][ultimate_icon_list_item icon_type=\"custom\" icon_img=\"id^191|url^http://scopun.co.uk/projects/catering1/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Screen-Shot-2017-09-25-at-2.40.34-PM.png|caption^null|alt^null|title^Screen-Shot-2017-09-25-at-2.40.34-PM|description^null\" el_class=\"iconstyle\"]<strong> Multiple payment methods </strong>\r\n<span style=\"color: #8d9395;\">Payment via invoice or credit card.</span>[/ultimate_icon_list_item][/ultimate_icon_list][vc_empty_space height=\"150px\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row bg_type=\"bg_color\" bg_color_value=\"#f6f6f6\"][vc_column width=\"1/6\"][vc_empty_space][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"2/3\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"Pricing F.A.Q.\" font_container=\"tag:h1|text_align:center\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\"][vc_tta_accordion][vc_tta_section active=\"1\" title=\"What is a scan profile?\" tab_id=\"1506334786665-c88509b4-f20a\"][vc_column_text]A scan profile can be a domain, subdomain or IP address you own. The great thing about scan profiles is that you customize them with different configurations so, for example, you can scan the same domain with different credentials. Our pricing is based on the number of scan profiles you add.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=\"What is included in the price?\" tab_id=\"1506334786751-d24baf2b-0b2e\"][vc_column_text]Unlimited scans, tool integrations, a constantly updated service - capable of detecting a massive amount of vulnerabilities.\r\nLearn more about all features.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=\"Can I change my subscription at any time?\" tab_id=\"1506334831647-6cfb0ac8-b043\"][vc_column_text]Yes, your subscription can be manually adjusted through the interface at any time or by emailing our support. The plan will be adjusted for next payment period.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=\"Can I delete my account at any time?\" tab_id=\"1506334851058-588a78df-9b87\"][vc_column_text]Yes. All data (test results, payment history and configuration) is owned by the user and can be deleted directly on the customer\'s request.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=\"What payment methods do you accept?\" tab_id=\"1506334867514-5bd47ac4-f50b\"][vc_column_text]We accept credit card (Visa, MasterCard, Maestro, American Express, Diners Club) and annual invoices.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=\"Do you have any discounts for nonprofit organizations?\" tab_id=\"1506334883634-6c8e419e-1e2e\"][vc_column_text]Nonprofit organizations can run one scan profile for free with unlimited use. Read our guidelines on what we consider a non-profit organization, and contact us if you believe you fit the profile.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][/vc_tta_accordion][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/6\"][vc_empty_space][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row content_placement=\"middle\" height=\"auto\" width=\"full\" el_class=\"nonprofitafterfaq\"][vc_column text_color=\"#ffffff\" width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1537260977009{padding-right: 150px !important;padding-left: 150px !important;background-color: #f36c21 !important;}\"][vc_empty_space height=\"50px\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"Nonprofit organizations\" font_container=\"tag:h2|text_align:center\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\"][vc_column_text]If you have a private project or are a non-profit organization you can run one scan profile for free with unlimited use. What are you waiting for?[/vc_column_text][us_btn text=\"Contact Us with a Request\" style=\"outlined\" color=\"white\" align=\"center\"][vc_empty_space height=\"50px\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1506335659118{padding-right: 150px !important;padding-left: 150px !important;}\"][vc_empty_space height=\"50px\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"Still not convinced?\" font_container=\"tag:h2|text_align:center\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\"][vc_column_text]Unlimited use, tests for +500 attacks and tool integrations. If you’re still not convinced have a look on what’s under the hood.[/vc_column_text][us_btn text=\"Learn more\" style=\"outlined\" color=\"contrast\" align=\"center\"][vc_empty_space height=\"50px\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Subscription', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'subscription', '', '', '2018-09-18 09:01:26', '2018-09-18 09:01:26', '', 0, 'http://scopun.co.uk/projects/catering1/?page_id=188', 0, 'page', '', 0),
